ComicInfo.Title: Chapter Eleven: Something In The Night
ComicInfo.Summary: This issue, SEX goes even deeper than ever before! Simon Cooke faces his adulthood. Japanese businessmen get their freak on. Annabelle reprimands an employee. Then there's the battle cry heard throughout the underworld: "Breaks! Damn straight!" This one's a rub for the ages!
